snippet.title: SuperSmash: Physics Battle - Trailer
snippet.description:
Play now! https://store.steampowered.com/app/1077290/SuperSmash_Physics_Battle/

SuperSmash is a physics base multiplayer fighting game.Character is fully driven by physics engine,and there are lots of different weapons and maps.It will provide you totally different battle experience.
